      "name": "Dolsot-Style Stone Bowl",
      "amount": "1",
      "notes": "Preheated"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a medium saucepan, bring the water to a gentle boil.",
    "Add the oats, ginger, and chili flakes, stirring constantly to prevent lumps.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the oats have absorbed most of the water.",
    "Add the score-fat, sea salt, and black pepper, stirring until well combined.",
    "Add the steamed broccoli to the saucepan and stir gently to distribute.",
    "Spoon the porridge mixture into the preheated dolsot-style stone bowl.",
    "Drizzle with lemon juice and sprinkle with green onions and fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
